      <title>风险偏好反弹，比特币五日内首次上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/bitcoin-rises-for-first-time-in-5-days-as-risk-appetite-rebounds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储维持利率稳定后，交易员对风险资产的兴趣出现反弹，比特币五天来首次上涨。]]></description>
