    <item>
      <title>艾伯塔省计划设立 1730 亿美元基金，摆脱对石油收入的依赖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/alberta-targets-173-billion-heritage-fund-to-wean-itself-off-oil-revenue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大最大的石油生产省份阿尔伯塔省计划到 2050 年将其财富基金增加约 10 倍，达到 2500 亿加元（1730 亿美元），以摆脱对不稳定的自然资源收入的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/alberta-targets-173-billion-heritage-fund-to-wean-itself-off-oil-revenue</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 21:15:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
